{"tid":1211373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有一個可以取代tg嘅溝通渠道","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T20:51:36.000Z","uid":249971,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9abdd1b5b4251255733a282699dea846aa66a83f","tid":1211373,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:36:19.000Z","msg":"（幫推）<br />\n啱啱大家都應該知道telegram公海谷主畀人拉咗同埋俾大量黑客入侵緊既消息，telegram絕對唔夠安全同埋保密，同埋最重要係太多唔同嘅group令到所有人嘅資訊太過混亂，前線同埋後勤資訊無限重疊。Discord最好地方係<br />\n1)可以一個地方開幾個CHANNEL，唔洗分散幾十個GROUP 討論，同時可以切換版面睇唔同類型嘅資訊<br />\n2)可以分channel@分工合作，前線同埋後勤可以分開討論，可以及時提醒前線人員狗賊最新動態，同時又唔洗比物資內容洗版<br />\n3)同時可以控制權限，控制唔同人睇到嘅野，咁樣係確定個個人唔係狗賊嘅時侯先睇到多d資訊，唔係就淨係睇到公海資訊<br />\n4)discord唔洗大家留手機，開個垃圾email就可以，比較安全&amp;nbsp;<br />\n5)最重要可以即時多人通訊，保持機動性，大家係撤退嘅時候可以保持通訊，唔駛各自跑。<br />\n6)最後係最危險嘅情況下谷主可以delete成個group，無人會查到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAndroid:<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/discord/id985746746%3Fmt%3D8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwio3MvkmuTiAhUotlkKHcYkD_kQFjABegQIBRAC&amp;usg=AOvVaw0YMYYLbiqr7eLknLeYorCd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fdiscord%2Fid985746746%253Fmt%253D8%26ved%3D2ahUKEwio3MvkmuTiAhUotlkKHcYkD_kQFjABegQIBRAC%26usg%3DAOvVaw0YMYYLbiqr7eLknLeYorCd&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvxSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=65ed930e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/discord/id985746746%3Fmt%3D8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwio3MvkmuTiAhUotlkKHcYkD_kQFjABegQIBRAC&amp;usg=AOvVaw0YMYYLbiqr7eLknLeYorCd</a><br />\nIOS:<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/discord/id985746746%3Fmt%3D8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwio3MvkmuTiAhUotlkKHcYkD_kQFjABegQIBRAC&amp;usg=AOvVaw0YMYYLbiqr7eLknLeYorCd\" da